Class LocalizedPhenomenon

java.lang.Object
  environmentalSimulator.LocalizedPhenomenon
All Implemented Interfaces:
MeteorologicalPhenomenon
Direct Known Subclasses:
Thermal
public abstract class LocalizedPhenomenon
extends java.lang.Object
implements MeteorologicalPhenomenon

This class represents all the localized phenomena which can be implemented by the user. For the moment, only the following phenomena are treated : - thermal columns.
